        <mxCell id="legend" value="Readings flow left → up into the hub. The owner talks to the box; ConvoAI does ASR/LLM/TTS and function-calls the hub&#39;s MCP tools over public HTTPS. Deterministic answers come from Core+SQLite; general VN-utility questions go to the ADK agent on Vertex AI with Google Search grounding. Dashed red edge = the act loop." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=4;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#cccccc;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
